Phase 3: Mining & Staking Infrastructure

1. Mining Core (4 weeks)
   ├── MiningBase
   │   ├── PoW implementation
   │   ├── PoS implementation
   │   └── Hybrid system
   │
   ├── MiningPool
   │   ├── Pool creation
   │   ├── Reward distribution
   │   └── Pool governance
   │
   └── GreenMining
       ├── Energy tracking
       ├── Carbon offsetting
       └── Efficiency rewards

2. Staking System (3 weeks)
   └── StakingModule
       ├── Flexible staking
       ├── Reward calculation
       └── Unstaking mechanisms